Package org.bluezoo.gumdrop.telemetry.metrics

Class MetricData

java.lang.Object
org.bluezoo.gumdrop.telemetry.metrics.MetricData
public final class MetricData extends Object
Represents an aggregated metric ready for export. Contains the metric identity, type, and data points.
Author:
Chris Burdess
